{"tid":436630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人入侵紙皮界，同阿婆爭紙皮執","createTime":"2017-10-15T09:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T18:13:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9559bd3e06d074092fb5198c44f7e4c1a5806f","tid":436630,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171015/large/1508057556_ba45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171015%2Flarge%2F1508057556_ba45.jpg&h=d5641d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月中回收商停收廢紙三日，上水、灣仔多區出現「紙皮山」，默默無聞紙皮婆婆原來足以左右城市面貌。她們每日遊走大街小巷，彎腰執拾廢紙，換取微薄收入。在上水拾紙皮的黃婆婆指，近年多了內地人來港執紙皮，破壞早已劃分清楚的地盤。她指執紙皮靠平日與店舖建立互助關係，有紙皮婆婆「退休」後，將地盤過繼給她。<br />\n<br />\n黃婆婆指執紙皮公公、婆婆互不相識，大家各有地盤、互不騷擾。自己平日接收連鎖餅店掉棄的紙箱外，平日會清理水貨客留在店外的垃圾，亦會協助店舖看守卸下的月餅，試過在棄置紙箱發現貨物，自己會物歸原主，慢慢與店員建立交情，「你估淨係執紙皮咁簡單？」<br />\n每日執紙皮只賺到數十元，有店舖廢紙回收價每公斤1元，但黃婆婆卻將廢紙賣予每公斤8毫的店舖，「我之前同佢借車唔見三架手推車，佢又冇要我賠......好似我欠佢一份人情囉，所以明知佢（回收價）平都賣畀佢。」<br />\n黃婆婆指執紙皮地盤靠「繼承」，例如有紙皮婆婆專門執拾快餐店紙皮，後來退休湊孫，便介紹她接手執紙皮。不過，近年有內地人來港執紙皮，令中港矛盾延伸至執紙皮界，雙方為執紙皮屢起衝突，試過有老伯搶去紙皮並舉拳恫嚇，餅店女店員出面維護，「（店舖）入面嘅小姐話你走啦，我唔會畀你架。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171015/57333016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171015%2F57333016&d=RvflC8M4JOGOVo1dpxl6kNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=22d68410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171015%2F57333016&h=d56294b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171015/57333016</a>"},{"pid":"dc9513cf8ef3f154a959d051da3fdde2c9ad488d","tid":436630,"uid":21432,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"支那狗有無工作簽証？屌佢老母成班都係仆街黎"},{"pid":"807775928e6522ce65fd2071e136842300474158","tid":436630,"uid":30169,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政治唔關我事，唔好阻我搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f5c45b79b6498c39229f3255ec82945d7a136c","tid":436630,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f4b648d4f11c801a6f0181b12fefd98b915efcf1","tid":436630,"uid":29702,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70f4b150a333ac1479251f4db45b059b76a21ab8","tid":436630,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"行乞集團改行執紙皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e78fe6ccef009f6675a9a428705e732b4728b8","tid":436630,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"2c6b1bc2a1b4fcf8e5371253bd6b88eee2acdfff","tid":436630,"uid":30169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢老屎都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d27e60bfd1fd8803c4cb4aa759cff721afd98ee","tid":436630,"uid":10894,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:18:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf340c7fe462201b26d46b98c49797baa1eda564","tid":436630,"uid":14333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"「你估淨係執紙皮咁簡單？」<br />\n有幾撚難呀"},{"pid":"b12904c3dd27878c1f1e42754be4fb25f666de12","tid"